{"tid":761840,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友同我講佢有諗過偷食","createTime":"2018-07-30T17:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T12:51:59.000Z","uid":66321,"like":4,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b52ad047320b101cf27be856ce23a9cff0fa6f","tid":761840,"uid":66321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"同男朋友long d<br />\n係佢嗰到有個女仔成日都撩佢<br />\n佢今日話我知 佢有諗過同人flirt下玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔知咁樣算唔算想偷食出軌<br />\n但係佢最後都控制自己咩都冇做到<br />\n我聽到係咁喊 但佢話自己冇錯 係男人都會咁樣<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咩都冇做冇行動<br />\n但係我好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟係咪我唔夠好啊<br />\n係我太過執著多心，定係男仔有女朋友都會諗過同其他女仔玩下<br />\n我係咪應該睇開d <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec06d9998a59affe115d092bd35dfbba217ec2b","tid":761840,"uid":157669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:35:17.000Z","msg":"火車出軌"},{"pid":"54505302b648308d4539ffe6094afb1dd431465f","tid":761840,"uid":51989,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:35:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac80bf129e13a47e7fc4848b0ac24adf544f1918","tid":761840,"uid":47237,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"你放過人啦 人地唔想再搞基啦"},{"pid":"1e34370771afdebf624431972f25d6b98d907768","tid":761840,"uid":66321,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"ac80bf129e13a47e7fc4848b0ac24adf544f1918","tid":761840,"uid":47237,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"你放過人啦 人地唔想再搞基啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:37:45.000Z","msg":"真絲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 